	<h2>Steps to Create and Run Servlet/JSP project - </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Download the tools for eclipse J2EE development and Tomcat 
			server adapter</li>
		<li>Download tomcat and create a new server in eclipse to work with
			installed version of tomcat</li>
		<li>Create new Dynamic web project</li>
		<li>Configure build path if not already done with servlet-api.jar</li>
		<li>Edit web.xml file for welcome file and servlet mappings</li>
		<li>Create first servlet and JSP files</li>
		<li>Run with the tomcat server installed</li>
	</ol>
